    "tStartMs": 9690,
    "dDurationMs": 3540,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "these big companies are putting online.\nI think now's the time to get into it,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13350,
    "dDurationMs": 1590,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but are you ready? In my."
