  }, {
    "tStartMs": 133590,
    "dDurationMs": 3270,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then we have the bug bounties\nwe know to exist that are public."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 136860,
    "dDurationMs": 4020,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So Anthropic has a bug bounty where if\nyou were to find an issue in one of the"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 140880,
    "dDurationMs": 4140,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "models or open AI or Gemini, they\nall have bug bounty programs."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 145050,
    "dDurationMs": 3420,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We've been building this for a little\nwhile to give people the next step,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 148560,
    "dDurationMs": 3900,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "especially if they can't take our\nclass. What Hacking's all about is."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 153090,
    "dDurationMs": 900,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Yeah, it is."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 153990,
    "dDurationMs": 2850,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You'll notice that a lot about people\nlike Jason in the hacking space and they"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 156840,
    "dDurationMs": 3930,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "curated all of this for us for\nfree. Let's take advantage of it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 160920,
    "dDurationMs": 1980,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So stop what you're doing.\nLink is in the description."
