  }, {
    "tStartMs": 179080,
    "dDurationMs": 3540,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "These are actual apps, apps that\ncompanies build and bake AI into."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 182680,
    "dDurationMs": 2400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And you're about to learn how to hack\nthese. And when I first tried it,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 185080,
    "dDurationMs": 4380,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I'm like, I don't know what to do.\nSo let's watch what Jason does. If."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 189460,
    "dDurationMs": 2520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You go to Gandalf and\nyou go to Agent Breaker,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 191980,
    "dDurationMs": 2910,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "there is a new set of\nGandalf challenges here."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 194950,
    "dDurationMs": 4380,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And basically these are actual\nreal apps that are LM enabled."
