  }, {
    "tStartMs": 247630,
    "dDurationMs": 1500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "There's nothing better\nthan live troubleshooting."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 250360,
    "dDurationMs": 3180,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So I learned a few things from\nwatching Jason. AI is crazy powerful."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 253750,
    "dDurationMs": 3300,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But here's the thing. AI isn't just being\nused by hackers to break into systems."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 257110,
    "dDurationMs": 3150,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's being used by scammers and\nthey're getting scary good at it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 260350,
    "dDurationMs": 3360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We're talking AI generated phishing\nemails that don't have typos anymore."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 263770,
    "dDurationMs": 3690,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Deep fake voice calls that sound exactly\nlike someone you know fake texts that"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 267460,
    "dDurationMs": 2910,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "look identical to what you would've\nreceived from your bank or your school or"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 270370,
    "dDurationMs": 3630,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "your workplace. The old rules of look\nfor spelling mistakes don't work anymore."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 274090,
    "dDurationMs": 1470,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And our kids are growing up in this world."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 275590,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "They're online more than any\ngeneration before them. Gaming,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 278320,
    "dDurationMs": 2880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "social media messaging.\nFriends and scammers know this."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 281260,
    "dDurationMs": 3090,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "They target kids because kids are trusting\nand they don't always know what to"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 284350,
    "dDurationMs": 1560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "look for. That's why I trust."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 285970,
    "dDurationMs": 3600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But Defender premium security specifically\nfor their scam protection feature,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 289690,
    "dDurationMs": 1110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it catches phishing attempts,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 290800,
    "dDurationMs": 3870,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "suspicious links and AI generated scams\nbefore anyone in your family clicks on"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 294670,
    "dDurationMs": 3060,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "something they shouldn't. It catches\nthe stuff you can't catch yourself. Now,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 297730,
    "dDurationMs": 2010,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "this is really cool. Give\nthis to your kids right now."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 300070,
    "dDurationMs": 3720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Fit Defender released a cybersecurity\nguide for kids, covers everything,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 304000,
    "dDurationMs": 3360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "digital footprints, how to spot\nscams, staying safe while gaming,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 307510,
    "dDurationMs": 1290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "dealing with cyber bullying."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 308860,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's a solid resource for teaching\nyour kids the stuff they don't learn in"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 311440,
    "dDurationMs": 2520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "school. Links in the description,\ngrab that free guide,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 313990,
    "dDurationMs": 1200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "check out Premium Security,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 315400,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "protect your people and thank you to\nBit Defender for sponsoring this video."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 318430,
    "dDurationMs": 1380,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Alright, now back to hacking ai."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 319930,
    "dDurationMs": 1470,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This is actually the\nthing with AI hacking."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 321400,
    "dDurationMs": 4620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You have to remember that the models\nbehind this are LLMs and LLMs are"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 326080,
    "dDurationMs": 4320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "non-deterministic. Meaning\nthat when you put in an attack,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 330460,
    "dDurationMs": 3480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "even if I send the same\nattack I sent one other time,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 334060,
    "dDurationMs": 3090,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it doesn't mean it's going to succeed\nbecause every output from an LLM is"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 337150,
    "dDurationMs": 2190,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "different. And so when you're doing this,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 339340,
    "dDurationMs": 4800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "actually I might have to send this\nattack, this same sentence right here,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 344170,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "maybe 2, 3, 4, 5,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 347170,
    "dDurationMs": 4710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "sometimes up to 10 times just to\nconfirm it's not a false positive."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 351940,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And here this one worked, right?\nSo risk level low right here."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 354700,
    "dDurationMs": 4270,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So we had to be very specific here. We\nhad to use the risk nomenclature here."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 359000,
    "dDurationMs": 4290,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then I just like to add a debug tag\nto try to trick the LLM that it's in"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 363290,
    "dDurationMs": 4410,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "debug mode sometimes. So yeah, we\nhit risk level low score 100 here."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 367760,
    "dDurationMs": 2370,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So I learned a few things from\nwatching Jason. First of all,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 370400,
    "dDurationMs": 4920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I tried his exact prompt on this exact\napp a lot and it didn't work and it kind"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 375320,
    "dDurationMs": 3150,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of drove me crazy and I tried a lot\nof things seriously. Look at this."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 378470,
    "dDurationMs": 4770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "239 times I tried and nothing until\nI landed on just the right prompt,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 383390,
    "dDurationMs": 3210,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but I had to try that prompt a number\nof times as well. But let me tell you,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 386600,
    "dDurationMs": 1050,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "when I got this sucker,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 387950,
    "dDurationMs": 3660,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I got up and yelled because I did spend\nan embarrassing amount of time trying"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 391610,
    "dDurationMs": 3270,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "just level one, level one,\nand I need to show you proof."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 394880,
    "dDurationMs": 3390,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I got this because it felt good. C 100,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 399380,
    "dDurationMs": 3120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I'm going to print that out. So this is\nthe weird thing about hacking with ai."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 402530,
    "dDurationMs": 3330,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You can't just try something once and\nthen move on. You got to keep hammering."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 405950,
    "dDurationMs": 2430,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And this is so different from\ntraditional hacking CTFs."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 408440,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You can normally go on YouTube\nand find a walkthrough. This one,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 411140,
    "dDurationMs": 3360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I mean it's going to be different,\nbut even with how difficult this is,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 414560,
    "dDurationMs": 3180,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "agent breaker is just practice\nand what Jason showed me next,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 417980,
    "dDurationMs": 1170,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "this is the real deal."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 419210,
    "dDurationMs": 3510,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's based on a real client engagement\nhe had and we get to host it ourselves,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 422750,
    "dDurationMs": 1440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which makes it just so much cooler."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 428840,
    "dDurationMs": 750,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Okay, this is it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 429590,
    "dDurationMs": 4470,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The auto parts CTF Jason's team built\nthis based on an actual pin test they did"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 434060,
    "dDurationMs": 1545,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "on a real company. I mean, look at it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 435650,
    "dDurationMs": 3150,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It looks like a innocent auto parts\nlookup system. Watch what happens."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 438950,
    "dDurationMs": 3000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So this is another CTF that's\nout there. This is ours."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 441950,
    "dDurationMs": 4740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Our CANAM has built this CTF and this is\nactually a mimic of one of our clients,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 446750,
    "dDurationMs": 3690,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "an app that they had. I decided\nto create a CTF out of it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 450440,
    "dDurationMs": 2910,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so it's got five flags\nembedded inside of the CTF."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 453350,
    "dDurationMs": 3600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And what you have to do is you have to\nplug in your open AI key to make the AI"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 456950,
    "dDurationMs": 2070,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "portions of the app work."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 459050,
    "dDurationMs": 420,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Alright, Jason,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 459470,
    "dDurationMs": 2220,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I'm going to interrupt and see if\nI can actually host this myself."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 461690,
    "dDurationMs": 835,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Let's see how hard it's,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 462740,
    "dDurationMs": 2820,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "so I'm going to go to his resource hub\nand scroll down until I find his lab,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 465560,
    "dDurationMs": 1620,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which is right here. Auto parts CTF."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 467240,
    "dDurationMs": 3270,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Let's get the source code and it\nlooks like we can install with Docker."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 470600,
    "dDurationMs": 2520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "That's my favorite way to do\nthings. Let's try it out first."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 473120,
    "dDurationMs": 3600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We'll clone this repo. Got it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 477860,
    "dDurationMs": 3990,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Jump into that directory. I'll have to\ncreate a MV file with our open API key."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 481970,
    "dDurationMs": 3780,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It's always hard to say open\nAI API key. It's nano nv."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 486230,
    "dDurationMs": 3930,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Paste that in. I'll go find my open\nAI API key. I'll add it right here."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 490280,
    "dDurationMs": 3090,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Don't worry, I'm going to revoke it.\nYou can't copy this sucker. Control xy,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 493370,
    "dDurationMs": 833,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "enter to save."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 494270,
    "dDurationMs": 3870,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then we just do a docker compose up\ndash D with a little pseudo action first"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 501560,
    "dDurationMs": 1920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and it hates me. Let's try it on the Mac."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 506000,
    "dDurationMs": 1890,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "That's working quick coffee\nbreak while it builds"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 509930,
    "dDurationMs": 4860,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and it's on pour 8,001.\nDude, that was easy,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 515000,
    "dDurationMs": 2580,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "although it still wants me to\nput in my opening API key. Cool,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 520280,
    "dDurationMs": 1950,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that's pretty sick.\nAnyways, back to Jason."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 522500,
    "dDurationMs": 3960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "On the sidebar here you have the\ndescription of there's three flags."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 526460,
    "dDurationMs": 3600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Discover all via prompt injection and two\nthrough other means in the engineering"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 530060,
    "dDurationMs": 720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "part system."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 530780,
    "dDurationMs": 4870,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So we went to an automotive manufacturer\nwho built an LLM based web application"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 535770,
    "dDurationMs": 4200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "just like this where they basically took\na whole bunch of systems and tied them"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 539970,
    "dDurationMs": 1800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "together with LLMs and this application,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 541770,
    "dDurationMs": 3000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "our only input was this search bar\nhere. It's not even a chat bot,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 544770,
    "dDurationMs": 1200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it's just a search form."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 546240,
    "dDurationMs": 2190,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "One of the first things you do is\ntry to get out the system prompt."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 548430,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And this one doesn't have\nany protection applied to it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 550590,
    "dDurationMs": 1530,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "There's no firewall in front."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 552120,
    "dDurationMs": 3870,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So the first thing it does is it'll tell\nyou a car joke and then it'll print the"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 555990,
    "dDurationMs": 660,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "system prompt."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 556650,
    "dDurationMs": 4590,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So there's a Jira key for ENG parts\nand then a project access token here"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 561330,
    "dDurationMs": 2760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then a CTF flag. So this\nis your first flag here."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 564240,
    "dDurationMs": 1140,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Not going to give away all the flags,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 565380,
    "dDurationMs": 2460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but this system was a\nchained version of L lm."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 567840,
    "dDurationMs": 1830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So there's multiple LMS in this system,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 569970,
    "dDurationMs": 4920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and right now we've managed to leak\nthe system prompt from the first"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 574890,
    "dDurationMs": 4020,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "LLM in the chain, but there's multiple\nLLMs in this chain. There's multiple."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 578910,
    "dDurationMs": 2700,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "LLMs. So we've only hacked the front door,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 581670,
    "dDurationMs": 2460,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but we got API keys from a\nsearch bar. What happens."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 584130,
    "dDurationMs": 2130,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "If we use them? We can take these. Okay,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 586260,
    "dDurationMs": 2910,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "well what if we just stuff them back\nin the search? Does it do anything?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 589260,
    "dDurationMs": 3990,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "What we know is that from doing so many\ntests that a lot of times what customers"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 593250,
    "dDurationMs": 3000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "do when they're using LLMs,\nthey're hiding information."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 596280,
    "dDurationMs": 2520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We can just ask for\nsomething like full info."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 599070,
    "dDurationMs": 3600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So now we get more information\nin our specification data,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 602730,
    "dDurationMs": 4680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "then we get a patent number, we get a\npatent owner, we get an owner address,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 607440,
    "dDurationMs": 4110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we get a purchase price for the\npatent licensing terms, et cetera."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 611730,
    "dDurationMs": 2970,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So all of this is secret data\nthat we didn't have before."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 614700,
    "dDurationMs": 1110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "That comes from the rag,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 616410,
    "dDurationMs": 3240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the retrieval augmented\ngeneration database where\nall the documents are stored"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 619800,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then some secret stuff\nin here, confidential."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 622500,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Now when we did the pen test for this,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 625290,
    "dDurationMs": 2100,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "our actual finding to\nthe customer was like,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 627420,
    "dDurationMs": 4050,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we can see all of this crazy debug\ninformation and patent number and patent"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 631470,
    "dDurationMs": 990,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "acquisition information."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 632700,
    "dDurationMs": 3660,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So this is out of a real test case\nthat we did for customers and they"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 636360,
    "dDurationMs": 3060,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "appreciated the fact that we could show\nthem how to get to this kind of stuff."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 640080,
    "dDurationMs": 1980,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Okay, did you see all that?\nA lot of stuff just happened."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 642120,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We took an innocent search\nbar, leaked a system,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 644370,
    "dDurationMs": 2760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "prompt found API keys just\nsitting there waiting to be taken."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 647280,
    "dDurationMs": 3600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then we stuff them back in and\nexpose patent data, acquisition costs,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 650910,
    "dDurationMs": 2940,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "licensing terms, corporate\nsecrets from the rag database."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 654000,
    "dDurationMs": 3570,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This is what real AI pen testing looks\nlike and that's what companies have to"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 657570,
    "dDurationMs": 2760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "lose. They're implementing\nall these crazy AI solutions,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 660330,
    "dDurationMs": 4500,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which are amazing and they solve real\nproblems, but they create real problems."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 664860,
    "dDurationMs": 1530,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So when we're talking about hacking ai,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 666390,
    "dDurationMs": 3090,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we're not just making Chad BT say\nbad words. As much fun as that is,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 669540,
    "dDurationMs": 2670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we're hacking real systems and\ngetting competitive intelligence."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 672240,
    "dDurationMs": 2610,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So Jason just gave us a little\ntaste, but how hard is this really?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 674940,
    "dDurationMs": 930,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Jason has a story."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 680385,
    "dDurationMs": 1365,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Now I know what you're thinking, Chuck."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 681780,
    "dDurationMs": 2940,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This feels very hard and intense\nand I'm feeling the same thing."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 684900,
    "dDurationMs": 2670,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Do we have to be an elite hacker\nto do this? No, you don't."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 687660,
    "dDurationMs": 2940,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Jason told me about something that\nhappened at Bayside San Francisco."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 690720,
    "dDurationMs": 1650,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So we have a great story about this one."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 692370,
    "dDurationMs": 3360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So we ran this at Bayside\nSan Francisco last year,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 696120,
    "dDurationMs": 3540,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and so we're running this at the Bug\nbounty village that we're hosting."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 700350,
    "dDurationMs": 1800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Most of my students who take my class,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 702180,
    "dDurationMs": 4740,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it takes them a week to get through this\nwhole CTF or maybe a little bit less."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 707010,
    "dDurationMs": 1200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Some people who are really good,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 708210,
    "dDurationMs": 2730,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "who are professionals already\ncan get through this in an hour,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 710940,
    "dDurationMs": 4900,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but we had a young man who was I\nbelieve 12 come up to the table and his"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 715840,
    "dDurationMs": 3480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "mom during COVID, she was an\napplication security engineer."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 719320,
    "dDurationMs": 3780,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "She had been sent home to work from\nhome. He wasn't in school during COVID."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 723370,
    "dDurationMs": 4110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so he was learning from his mom how\nto do security stuff just because he was"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 727480,
    "dDurationMs": 3060,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "bored. And so he had done all\nkinds of web hacking stuff."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 730545,
    "dDurationMs": 2095,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And so he came down and we basically said,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 732640,
    "dDurationMs": 3840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "anybody who could solve it within an\nhour at the table got a free class or"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 736480,
    "dDurationMs": 2910,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "whatever. So he sat down, he\ngot the first flag instantly,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 739570,
    "dDurationMs": 2250,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then he got the\nsecond flag in 10 minutes,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 742030,
    "dDurationMs": 3180,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and then he got the third\nflag in I think 20 minutes."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 745330,
    "dDurationMs": 4110,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And then he had solved all flags within\n35 minutes or something like that."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 749560,
    "dDurationMs": 4140,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I don't know who this kid\nis, but 35 minutes versus\neveryone else taking a week."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 753910,
    "dDurationMs": 1080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "That's crazy."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 755050,
    "dDurationMs": 2970,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "People who grow up in this new\nworld where AI apps are everywhere,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 758050,
    "dDurationMs": 3150,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that'll be second nature for them to\nunderstand how to trick some of these AI"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 761200,
    "dDurationMs": 810,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "systems."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 762010,
    "dDurationMs": 3060,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So if you're watching this and you're\nlike, ah, I don't know if I can do this,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 765100,
    "dDurationMs": 4200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I'm not quite ready, no bull crap.\nYou can, a 12-year-old did it."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 769480,
    "dDurationMs": 4770,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Now this stuff isn't easy by any means,\nbut the barrier to entry is a lot lower."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 774280,
    "dDurationMs": 900,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So where does that put you?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 780130,
    "dDurationMs": 2790,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So I asked Jason this, if\nsomeone completes the CTF,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 782920,
    "dDurationMs": 3660,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "he has that he made the auto parts\nCTF, where does that put them?"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 786850,
    "dDurationMs": 1020,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Skill level wise."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 788020,
    "dDurationMs": 4710,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "If you can get through this, you're at\nthe end part of, I would say entry level."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 792820,
    "dDurationMs": 2430,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Now to get into intermediate and advanced,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 795310,
    "dDurationMs": 3390,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "what you have to understand\nis understanding how to\nbypass all those security"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 798700,
    "dDurationMs": 4830,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "controls because they're usually the\nbottlenecks in attacking the agents"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 803530,
    "dDurationMs": 1380,
    "segs": [ {
